 Marx’ "Grundrissen der Kritik der politischen Ökonomie", seinen Artikeln für die "New-York Tribune" und Debatten mit Engels, in denen allesamt die Krise 1857/58 analysiert wird.   aThis volume includes Marx’s three previously unpublished "Crisis notebooks" with excerpts, newspaper clippings, and notes dating from the first world economic crisis in 1857–1858. The Crisis notebooks are closely connected to Marx’s Foundations of the Critique of Political Economy (Grundrisse), his articles for the New York Tribune, and debates with Engels – all of which analyze the 1857–1858 crisis.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 4a1857/1858. 4aCritique of Political Economy. 4aKrise. 4aKritik der Politischen Ökonomie. 4aPanic of 1857. 4aWeltwirtschaftskrise. 4acrisis. 4aworldwide economic depression. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / Modern.2bisacsh1 aFiehler, Fritz1 aGraßmann, Timm1 aHecker, Rolf, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMori, Kenji, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aOmura, Izumi, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTamaoka, Atsushi, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2017z9783110548228oZDB-23-DPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMEGA 1975-2019z9783110688139oZDB-23-GKO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMEGA Prepaid 1975-2032z9783110691986oZDB-23-GKO0 cprintz978311051765140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311056128940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110561289423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/co